Abundance matrix from phyloseq object

Retrieves the taxon abundance table from phyloseq-class object and ensures it is returned as taxa x samples matrix.

abundances(x, transform = "identity")

Arguments

x
phyloseq-class object
transform
Transformation to apply. The options include: 'compositional' (ie relative abundance), 'Z', 'log10', 'hellinger', 'identity', 'clr', 'ilr', or any method from the vegan::decostand function.

Value

Abundance matrix.

References

See citation('microbiome')

Examples

  data(dietswap)
  abundances(dietswap)
